Fun w/ SHROOMS! - Magic Circle ►► http://bit.ly/GTLshrooms
Warning: Some in game content may not be suitable for all audiences.

The Deep Web is a dark and creepy place - and I'm diving in head first! - in "Welcome to the Game." I'll have to solve puzzles, stop hackers, and muster all the courage I can find to try and survive the darkest recesses of the human collective mind. I'm almost too afraid to go on. Some people are just SOOO F'ed Up!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
